  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a claypot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add diced carrot and potato, cook for 5 minutes, or until they start to soften.",
    "Add chicken broth, bay leaves, black pepper, and salt. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Add sweetcorn to the claypot, cover, and simmer for another 10-15 minutes, or until the sweetcorn is tender.",
    "Stir in lemon juice and parsley. Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh dill and serve hot with a dollop of sour cream.",
    "Serve the stew in a claypot or individual bowls."
  ],
